Class ShrgList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.ScrollPaneConstants

    public class ShrgList
extends javax.swing.JScrollPane
    The most important gui object that hosts either a list of tools available to be pushed on the project structure lists, or, right the latters, a container that enumerates something specific to the project being designed; in this case the order in which the items are listed may have crucial impact on the resulting project or no impact: the list will be associated with a JSONArray or a JSONObject respectively.
